Release 1:
 * Parse command line arguments
 * Daemon mode
 * Store channel and user data in memory
 * Give scripts access to a complete IRC api
   + Channel.getTopic()
   + Channel.getUsers()
   + Channel.getMode()
   + Channel.isOp()
   + User.getNick()
   + User.getIdent()
   + User.getDesc()
   + User.getHost()
   + User.isAway()
   + User.getAwayMessage()
   + User.whois()
   + Channel[] User.getChannels()
   + IRC.join(channel)
   + IRC.part(channel, message)
   + IRC.quit(message)
   + IRC.action(channel, message)
   + IRC.topic(channel, topic)

Release 2:
 * Shared module support
